des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your “light”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “KLD Smart Living” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “KLD Smart Living” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “KLD Smart Living” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “KLD Smart Living” skill, and you'll be navigated to “KLD Smart Living” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, Turn On The Bedroom Light.”
“Alexa, Turn Off The Bedroom Light.”
“Alexa, Set The Bedroom Light To 50%.”
“Alexa, Brighten The Bedroom Light To 50%.”
“Alexa, Dim The Bedroom Light To 60%%.”
"Alexa, Set Bedroom Light To Green."
"Alexa, Set Bedroom Light To Warm."
